name: Micheal Blaine
description:
Am a down to earth man, loving, kind, sincere, outgoing and open minded, I like movies, cinemas, dancing, travelling, meeting and making people laugh I dislike liars and proud people.
Am looking for a living, kind, sincere and happy woman. I don’t care about shapes, sizes or looks in a woman all am after is a woman with a heart who is ready to love and be loved
